name: Squedge_Eepsey
content: Squedge Eepsey was a male Duros who lived in the city of Sahl-Evin on the planet Jenenma. Eepsey was a patron of the cantina The Hutt's Last Laugh in the Blinders district of Sahl Evin, and at some point during galactic history, a group of agents visited the cantina and encountered Eepsey. The Duros advised the individuals to avoid the cantina's fighting circle.
